    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The issue is that when only attaching, we create a lightweight JS interpreter (https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/develop/cmd/geth/main.go#L429), and we do not pass an ethereum configuration (which contains the actual datadir parameter) to it. Hence setting the data dir (https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/develop/cmd/geth/js.go#L439) never happens. The solution would be to extract the needed configuration options manually and pass them to the lightweight JSRE too.\n",
